Shakespeare, Harry Potter, The Quotations of Chairman Mao and Mickey

00:02:06.590 --> 00:02:11.910
Mouse, I would be very impressed if you said that they had all been banned.

00:02:12.952 --> 00:02:17.502
They have, all for very different reasons, at different times, in different

