00:23:46.892 --> 00:23:49.612
But it is almost always a bad idea.

00:23:50.242 --> 00:23:52.812
So, what can we take from all of this?

00:23:53.522 --> 00:23:59.474
Firstly, it’s that banning a book is almost always a badge of shame for a country.

00:23:59.854 --> 00:24:05.074
We only need to look at the countries that have done it in the past, and those that are doing

00:24:05.074 --> 00:24:11.784
